<i>noun</i>: 경박 [경박], 경망 [경망] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>경박 [경박]</dt><br>
<dd>frivolity; flippancy; insincerity</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 조심스럽지 못하고 가벼움.</dd><br>
<dd>A lack of caution and gravity in words and or actions.</dd><br>
<dt>경망 [경망]</dt><br>
<dd>flippancy; frivolity; carelessness; hastiness; imprudence</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 가볍고 조심스럽지 못함.</dd><br>
<dd>A remark or behavior being light and careless.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>